    <item>
      <title>OpenAI 将向 Axel Springer 支付数千万美元以使用新闻内容</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-13/openai-axel-springer-ink-deal-to-use-news-content-in-chatgpt</link>
      <description><![CDATA[ChatGPT 制造商 OpenAI 已同意向 Axel Springer SE 支付数千万欧元，以获得使用这家媒体巨头的新闻文章和内容来构建其人工智能系统的权利。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-13/openai-axel-springer-ink-deal-to-use-news-content-in-chatgpt</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 13 Dec 2023 14:53:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Airbnb 将支付 5.76 亿欧元以和解意大利税务索赔</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-13/airbnb-agrees-to-pay-576-million-to-settle-italian-tax-claim</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Airbnb Inc. 的爱尔兰子公司同意向意大利当局支付 5.76 亿欧元（6.21 亿美元），以了结其未缴纳足够税款的指控。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-13/airbnb-agrees-to-pay-576-million-to-settle-italian-tax-claim</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 13 Dec 2023 12:20:10 GMT</pubDate>
